00:02:28.970 --> 00:02:35.264
was the last major migration
of refugees into America.

00:02:35.264 --> 00:02:36.680
We haven't had
another recent one,

00:02:36.680 --> 00:02:39.080
and I think that the
Vietnamese-American community

00:02:39.080 --> 00:02:43.280
can be seen as an example
of the incredible benefits

00:02:43.280 --> 00:02:46.125
and richness that can
happen when you are generous

00:02:46.125 --> 00:02:47.750
