implications that it has

00:06:16.770 --> 00:06:19.530
and the ripple effects of
representation in media

00:06:19.530 --> 00:06:22.590
in everything-- everyone on
this panel is talking about--

00:06:22.590 --> 00:06:25.920
on immigration, on politics,
on the economy and leadership

00:06:25.920 --> 00:06:30.480
roles in companies like Google,
the bamboo ceiling, everything.

00:06:30.480 --> 00:06:34.894
